thread.title: Justin Graeff

author: Justin Graeff
title: Justin Graeff
text: Eeuroparts has done a great job of delivering the parts I need without spending a ton of money. I ordered the brake kit for my 9-5 and everything came as expected. I made the mistake of not realizing that my Aero didn't have the larger brakes in the back, so I ordered the Calipers a dew days later and everything arrived in a timely manner. I would definitely recommend Eeuroparts to anyone who asked!
